dr.evomodel.transmission
Class TransmissionHistoryModel

java.lang.Object
  dr.inference.model.AbstractModel
      dr.evomodel.transmission.TransmissionHistoryModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeColouringProvider, Units, Model, ModelListener, StatisticList, VariableListener, MPISerializable, Identifiable, java.io.Serializable
public class TransmissionHistoryModel
extends AbstractModel
implements TreeColouringProvider, Units

A model for defining a known transmission history. Times of transmission events can optionally be obtained as parameters for sampling. In future it may be possible to sample the direction of transmission where this is not known.
